Class ClauseNode

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.hg.Node
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.hg.CostNode
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.hg.ClauseNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<CostNode>
public class ClauseNode extends CostNode
A node which represents a conjunctive clause, a conjunction of atomic preconditions that must all have a finite cost before the clause can have a finite cost.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
